OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,F"Your intent was to kill and she would
OL,7,Fhave recognised that in those
OL,8,Fanguished moments when she fought for
OL,9,Fher life before you extinguished it."
OL,11,F"No sentence can restore life or ease
OL,12,Fthe suffering of those left behind."
OL,14,FThroughout the proceedings, Richard
OL,15,FJones kept his head bowed. As he was
OL,16,Fled from the dock, shouts of 'scumbag'
OL,17,Fcould be heard.
OL,19,FHe will serve a minimum term of 20
OL,20,Fyears.
