OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,FRichard Jones was found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder in January.
OL,9,FHe had denied murdering Sophie Evans,
OL,10,Fbut admitted manslaughter, saying he
OL,11,F'snapped' when he suspected the victim
OL,12,Fand her boyfriend, his son Jamie
OL,13,FDavies, were trying to defraud him.
OL,15,FThe court heard Jones visited Ms
OL,16,FEvans' home in Bigyn Road, Llanelli,
OL,17,Fat 9:19 am on 5 July 2024.
