OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,FHe was recorded on a doorbell camera
OL,7,Ftalking on the phone with Sophie
OL,8,Fbefore she opened the front door to
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FHe was inside the house for just 40
OL,12,Fminutes before CCTV captured him
OL,13,Frunning back to his car, returning to
OL,14,Fthe house and then driving off.
OL,16,FIn the moments before, he had attacked
OL,17,FSophie and left her for dead in her
OL,18,Fkitchen.
