OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,FAt 5:27 pm, police received a 999-call
OL,7,Freporting that Richard Jones had
OL,8,Fkilled Sophie Evans.
OL,10,FSophie's body was discovered on the
OL,11,Fkitchen floor and was confirmed dead.
OL,13,FFifteen minutes later, Jones texted
OL,14,Fhis ex-partner asking her not to say
OL,15,Fanything.
OL,17,FFollowing police enquiries, Jones was
OL,18,Ffound by officers near the entrance to
OL,19,FPembrey Country Park at 8pm.
