OL,3,CMan who murdered son's girlfriend in
OL,4,C'frenzied attack' gets life sentence
OL,6,FHe was arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,7,Fand taken to hospital where he
OL,8,Fremained for four days.
OL,10,FWhen he arrived in custody on 9 July
OL,11,F2024, Jones made a phone call to his
OL,12,Fmother in which he told her he had
OL,13,F"messed up again."
OL,15,FOfficers found handwritten notes by
OL,16,FJones saying, "I got scammed and
OL,17,Frinsed by my own son, so I dealt with
OL,18,Fit myself, I had no other choice."
OL,20,FOn 11 July, he was charged with the
OL,21,Fmurder of Sophie Evans.
