OL,6,FPaying tribute to Ms Evans, her family
OL,7,Fdescribed her "beautiful smile and
OL,8,Fcomforting ways".
OL,10,FThey said, "Our Sophie was a kind,
OL,11,Fcaring and wonderful mother, daughter,
OL,12,Fsister, and auntie.
OL,14,F"We all adored her. She was the rock
OL,15,Fof our family and the best mum to her
OL,16,Ftwo little girls. She lit up every
OL,17,Froom, gave the best advice and loved
OL,18,Fher family so much.
