OL,6,FToday Swansea Crown Court heard a
OL,7,Fvictim impact statement from the
OL,8,Fsister of Sophie Evans. Kerry Quinlan
OL,9,Fsaid "words could not express" how
OL,10,Fmuch her two young children miss her.
OL,12,F"When they cry themselves to sleep
OL,13,Fwanting their mum, she is not there
OL,14,Fand never will be."
OL,16,FDyfed-Powys Police Detective
OL,17,FSuperintendent Gareth Roberts said,
OL,18,F"My thoughts remain with Sophie's
OL,19,Ffamily, who have endured unimaginable
OL,20,Fheartbreak at the loss of their
OL,21,Fmother, daughter, sister and auntie.
