OL,6,F"Sophie's death was completely
OL,7,Favoidable, a result of senseless
OL,8,Fviolence triggered when Richard Jones
OL,9,Flost his temper.
OL,11,F"Sophie was vulnerable when Jones
OL,12,Fattacked, alone in her home with no
OL,13,Fmeans of defending herself. She was
OL,14,Fleft with fatal injuries when Jones
